{"_path":"/zh_hans/getting-started/template","_dir":{"_path":"/zh_hans/getting-started/template/_dir","title":"模板系统"},"_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"概述","description":"模板是指整个游戏工程打包作为一个模板分享或售卖给他人使用。","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"模板是指整个游戏工程打包作为一个模板分享或售卖给他人使用。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"模板可以基于GC内核进行二次开发制作，也可以使用Empty工程从零开始编写。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"目前尚未开放第三方制作的模板上传模板商城，请耐心等待。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"blockquote","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"GC可视化编辑器就是使用Empty编写并制作成了GC2D内核和GC2D网络内核"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n而ARPG-黑之书又是基于GC2D内核二次开发制作生成的ARPG单机游戏模板。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"alt text","src":"/image/zh_hans/getting-started/21.template/1.index/image.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"关于模板制作和购买的机制"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"关于模板制作和购买的机制"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如果某个模板是基于另一个模板开发制作的，那么作者在购买该模板时会要求已购买另一个父模板。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"也支持结算同时购买。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"blockquote","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"比如作者C使用《ARPG-黑之书》二次开发追加了N个模块功能再次售卖，购买者会要求已购买过《ARPG-黑之书》。\n比如使用A模板开发了B模板，而有人使用了B模板开发了C模板，那么购买C模板时会要求购买B和A。（直到根源）"}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"关于模板制作和购买的机制","depth":2,"text":"关于模板制作和购买的机制"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:zh_hans:getting-started:21.template:1.index.md","_source":"content","_file":"zh_hans/getting-started/21.template/1.index.md","_stem":"zh_hans/getting-started/21.template/1.index","_extension":"md"}